subSections.title: Etymology
subSections.text: From {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*s-wa-ŋ||to go; to come}}. Cognate with {{cog|my|ဝင်||to come in; to enter}}, {{cog|bo|འོང||to come}}, {{m|bo|ཡོང||to come}}. Related to {{och-l|于|to go}}.
